#Scrolling:

Enter scrolling/copy mode: Ctr-a esc
Scroll up: Ctrl-u
Scroll down Ctrl-d
Exist scrolling/copy mode: esc esc

#Create new screen with name
screen -S <screen name>

#Windows
Create new window:  Ctr-a c
See window list:  Ctr-a "
Rename current window:  Ctrl-a A
Change to last-visited window:   Ctrl-a Ctrl-a
